785
00:57:33,825 --> 00:57:37,871
Actually, I have a hard time
falling asleep because I'm sensitive.

786
00:57:37,954 --> 00:57:40,206
I don't think so.
You slept so well that day.

787
00:57:40,290 --> 00:57:41,749
Exactly.

788
00:57:41,833 --> 00:57:44,502
I think that it was because of your sofa.

789
00:57:44,586 --> 00:57:45,837
Weren't you sleeping just now?

790
00:57:45,920 --> 00:57:48,089
When I wake up, I can't fall asleep.

791
00:57:48,173 --> 00:57:49,424
You woke me up.

792
00:57:50,049 --> 00:57:51,676
So what's the model of your sofa?

793
00:57:51,759 --> 00:57:52,969
Tell me now.

794
00:57:53,052 --> 00:57:56,055
I'll take a look and let you know.

795
00:57:56,931 --> 00:57:59,058
What about tonight? You're already awake.

796
00:58:00,977 --> 00:58:03,938
Thanks to you,
I won't be sleeping tonight.

797
00:58:04,022 --> 00:58:05,356
Because of me?

798
00:58:07,275 --> 00:58:09,152
There's something that I do.

799
00:58:09,235 --> 00:58:13,406
Drinking warm milk helps me fall asleep.

800
00:58:13,490 --> 00:58:14,949
Why don't you try that?

801
00:58:16,993 --> 00:58:20,830
Don't expect everyone
to have milk at home.

802
00:58:23,374 --> 00:58:26,586
By any chance, do you have

803
00:58:26,669 --> 00:58:28,421
any other solution?

804
00:58:29,088 --> 00:58:31,591
Shall I read you a book?

805
00:58:31,674 --> 00:58:33,343
It always works on Byeol.

806
00:58:35,261 --> 00:58:36,429
Am I a child?

807
00:58:36,513 --> 00:58:38,515
- You're not that different--
- What?

808
00:58:38,598 --> 00:58:39,807
I'm sorry.

809
00:58:46,856 --> 00:58:48,274
I'll take care of it.

810
00:58:49,067 --> 00:58:50,818
I'll be hanging up now.

811
00:58:50,902 --> 00:58:51,819
Okay.

812
00:58:54,531 --> 00:58:55,365
Sleep well.

813
00:58:56,699 --> 00:58:57,659
Okay.

814
00:58:58,993 --> 00:59:00,078
Sleep well.

815
00:59:08,920 --> 00:59:10,547
Don't have nightmares.

816
01:00:08,688 --> 01:00:09,689
<i>Going up.</i>

817
01:00:11,399 --> 01:00:12,609
<i>The doors are closing.</i>

818
01:00:13,943 --> 01:00:15,111
Ms. Seo.

819
01:00:32,879 --> 01:00:34,672
What? You look pretty.

820
01:00:35,423 --> 01:00:36,841
Oh, thanks.

821
01:00:37,634 --> 01:00:38,760
Are you going somewhere tonight?

822
01:00:39,469 --> 01:00:40,678
- No.
- <i>Going up.</i>

823
01:00:42,055 --> 01:00:43,681
That's odd. You're pretty.

824
01:00:48,770 --> 01:00:50,313
Where are you going
so early in the morning?

825
01:00:50,396 --> 01:00:52,065
I was about to call you.

826
01:00:52,148 --> 01:00:53,024
Perfect timing.

827
01:00:53,107 --> 01:00:54,567
I'm borrowing Mr. Yu for the day.

828
01:00:54,651 --> 01:00:56,152
What is this about?

829
01:00:56,235 --> 01:00:57,987
Heonjo Group is planning on reorganizing.

830
01:00:58,071 --> 01:01:01,282
Mr. Yu has a lot of experience
since he worked in HR.

831
01:01:01,366 --> 01:01:04,118
It'd be favorable for us
to bring an expert.

832
01:01:04,202 --> 01:01:05,745
That's a good idea. Go with him.

833
01:01:06,621 --> 01:01:07,747
Where's Mr. Yu?

834
01:01:07,830 --> 01:01:09,582
He went downstairs to get ready.

835
01:01:09,666 --> 01:01:12,460
Our meeting might end late today.

836
01:01:12,543 --> 01:01:14,921
I'll let him get off work
right after the meeting.

837
01:01:18,675 --> 01:01:19,801
Ms. Kang?

838
01:01:19,884 --> 01:01:20,927
Yes?

839
01:01:21,511 --> 01:01:22,387
Oh, okay.

840
01:01:22,470 --> 01:01:24,263
- Go ahead and do that.
- Okay.

841
01:01:25,765 --> 01:01:28,726
Why are you so dressed up today?

842
01:01:30,103 --> 01:01:31,229
It's my usual outfit.

843
01:01:32,021 --> 01:01:33,022
Good luck.

844
01:01:36,609 --> 01:01:38,778
Something seems different about her.

845
01:02:19,444 --> 01:02:20,445
MESSAGE FROM YU EUN-HO

846
01:02:21,154 --> 01:02:22,822
<i>I'll be there on time.</i>

847
01:02:22,905 --> 01:02:24,157
<i>See you at the recital.</i>

848
01:02:31,372 --> 01:02:33,458
<i>Don't worry about useless things.</i>

849
01:02:33,541 --> 01:02:34,751
<i>Focus on the meeting.</i>

850
01:03:11,245 --> 01:03:13,664
Well, after that was in the clear,

851
01:03:13,748 --> 01:03:15,583
he was interviewed by the executives

852
01:03:15,666 --> 01:03:17,460
and passed through without a hitch.

853
01:03:17,543 --> 01:03:19,879
I'll contact them
and confirm the interview dates.

854
01:03:20,588 --> 01:03:21,714
Okay, that sounds good.

855
01:03:50,535 --> 01:03:51,661
What's gotten into her?

856
01:03:54,247 --> 01:03:55,081
Where is she going?

857
01:06:33,239 --> 01:06:34,532
<i>What kind of person</i>

858
01:06:35,533 --> 01:06:37,034
<i>is Yu Eun-ho to you?</i>

859
01:08:43,619 --> 01:08:45,746
<i>If they keep seeing each other,</i>

860
01:08:45,830 --> 01:08:47,414
<i>it means that they have feelings</i>
<i>for each other.</i>

861
01:08:48,040 --> 01:08:50,292
<i>What's wrong with falling?</i>
<i>You can get back up.</i>

862
01:08:50,376 --> 01:08:51,418
<i>I'll hold you.</i>

863
01:08:52,419 --> 01:08:56,465
<i>Ji-yun, did something happen to you?</i>
<i>Are you aware you aren't focused at work?</i>

864
01:08:56,549 --> 01:08:59,760
<i>I have someone who's on my mind.</i>

865
01:08:59,844 --> 01:09:01,303
<i>Have you checked</i>
<i>why she wants to change jobs?</i>

866
01:09:01,387 --> 01:09:02,763
<i>Dating at work?</i>

867
01:09:02,847 --> 01:09:04,348
<i>They broke up recently.</i>

868
01:09:04,431 --> 01:09:06,475
<i>She's having a hard time working with him.</i>

869
01:09:06,559 --> 01:09:09,186
<i>Get me a new secretary.</i>
<i>It interferes with my work.</i>

870
01:09:09,270 --> 01:09:10,688
<i>He keeps going over the line.</i>

871
01:09:10,771 --> 01:09:13,232
- <i>Ms. Kang, did I do something wrong?</i>
- I'm off.

872
01:09:13,315 --> 01:09:15,484
Mr. Yu, you didn't do anything wrong.

873
01:09:15,568 --> 01:09:16,443
I'm the problem.

874
01:09:17,570 --> 01:09:19,738
I like you, Eun-ho.

875
